  "title": "Sales Support Team (Training Provided)",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p>Ready to make an impact and lead a team towards success? We’re looking to expand our <strong>Sales Support Team</strong> to drive growth, engage audiences, and help take our brand to the next level.<br /></p><p>We work closely with clients from different industries, and help them to run their different marketing campaigns, to increase their sales revenue and brand awareness.</p><p><br /><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong><br /><br />- Engage and promote products and services to potential consumers<br />- Be the voice of the brand, crafting messages that captivate and convert<br />- Collaborate with the team to bring your ideas to life (yes, your ideas count!)<br />- Improving overall sales production and facilitate team growth</p><p><br /><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong><br /><br />- A natural leader with the drive to motivate and inspire<br />- Creative thinker who thrives on problem-solving<br />- Willing to learn and improve<br />- Immediate starters preferred</p><p><br /><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><p><br />- A collaborative and fun team that values creativity and fresh ideas<br />- A vibrant work culture<br />- Clear career progression<br />- Travelling opportunities<br />- Training!<br /></p><p>Ready to take charge and lead us to success?</p><p>Apply to find out more! 🌟</p>",
